sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant DSPA as DSPA / KFP API Server
    participant Init as Init Container
    participant SharedVol as Shared Volume<br/>/config/managed-pipelines/
    participant TaskPod as KFP Task Pod
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant HF as Hugging Face Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant PVC as Shared PVC<br/>(nfs-csi)
    participant LlamaStack as Llama Stack API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant ModelReg as Model Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Init,SharedVol: Flow 4: Init Container Startup
    Init->>Init: Read /app/managed-pipelines.json
    Init->>SharedVol: Copy compiled pipeline YAMLs
    DSPA->>SharedVol: Discover & register managed pipelines

    Note over User,ModelReg: Flow 1: AutoML Tabular Training
    User->>DSPA: Submit AutoML pipeline run
    DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule data loader pod
    TaskPod->>S3: Download dataset<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS IAM
    S3-->>TaskPod: Dataset CSV/Parquet
    TaskPod->>PVC: Write dataset to shared PVC
    DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule training pod (odh-automl image)
    TaskPod->>PVC: Read dataset, write model artifacts
    DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule leaderboard evaluation
    TaskPod->>PVC: Read model artifacts
    TaskPod->>DSPA: Store leaderboard as KFP artifact<br/>HTTPS/443, SA Token

    Note over User,ModelReg: Flow 2: Fine-Tuning (LoRA/SFT/OSFT)
    User->>DSPA: Submit fine-tuning pipeline run
    DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule dataset download pod
    TaskPod->>HF: Download model & dataset<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token
    HF-->>TaskPod: Model weights + dataset
    TaskPod->>PVC: Write to 50Gi PVC (RWX, nfs-csi)
    DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule training pod (GPU)
    TaskPod->>PVC: Read data, write fine-tuned model
    DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule lm-eval evaluation
    TaskPod->>PVC: Read model, run benchmarks
    DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule model registration
    TaskPod->>ModelReg: Register model with provenance<br/>HTTPS/443, Bearer Token

    Note over User,ModelReg: Flow 3: AutoRAG Optimization
    User->>DSPA: Submit AutoRAG pipeline run
    DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule document discovery pod
    TaskPod->>S3: List & download documents<br/>HTTPS/443, AWS IAM
    S3-->>TaskPod: PDF/DOCX/PPTX/HTML documents
    DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule text extraction (Docling)
    TaskPod->>TaskPod: Extract text (in-process Docling)
    DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule RAG optimization (odh-autorag image)
    TaskPod->>LlamaStack: Generate embeddings<br/>HTTPS/443, API Key
    LlamaStack-->>TaskPod: Document embeddings
    TaskPod->>TaskPod: Index in ChromaDB (in-process)
    TaskPod->>LlamaStack: LLM inference for evaluation<br/>HTTPS/443, API Key
    DSPA->>TaskPod: Schedule leaderboard evaluation
    TaskPod->>DSPA: Store RAG leaderboard as KFP artifact
